{
  "stem": "13079.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was contacting former graduates who had gone and obtained degrees or other expertise that could be used at West Point, asking if I was willing to come back to West Point and teach.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I, of course, told him I was not unmindful of my obligations, and I would be happy to.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was due to his letter of November of 1941 that I went back to West Point, and they took me in in the rank of a captain, which was the rank that my class held at that time.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I thought that was mighty fine of 'em.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I taught law there until I left to go overseas in February of 1945.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, when you were at West Point, was this is an equivalent rank, or were you wearing a uniform?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was wearing a uniform.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was back into Uncle Sam's arm.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the difference basically was in the number of cadets.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was-- there was only 1,200 cadets in the corps of cadets when I graduated, and there were 4,000 when I went back to teach there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were spread over the four years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, how many that would be for each class is a matter of arithmetic.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it was an expedited course.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had graduation in the winter, and they had a graduation in June.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So there were two graduation classes in each year that I was there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] To tell you frankly, I didn't know what a war crime was at that time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I knew-- we just had a smattering of Constitutional law, a little smattering of the conventions-- the Hague and Geneva Conventions.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were important [INAUDIBLE] because they do relate very much directly toward conduct of individuals, combatants and non-combatants.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
